snippet.title: Div. 4: Assumption 65, St. Mary Central 54 | Assumption beats St. Mary Central to advance in state basketball tournament
snippet.description: Alex Erdmann scored all of his 20 points in the first half to help Wisconsin Rapids Assumption take control and go on to beat Menasha St. Mary Central 65-54 Friday in the WIAA Division 4 boys state basketball semifinals. Madison - Alex Erdmann scored all of his 20
